parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoAnEx@.It’s been too long. She’s not returning.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoBaEx>.Have faith, brother. She has a plan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoAnOp>.And what would you suggest we do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoAnDe>.We will not use the Anachorismos. It was not her plan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoAnEx.We will give her one more week. If she does not return, we are using it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Don’t you see that big, ugly guy, and that demon?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuHaEx^.Lillian brought me here. She’s a demon! This is Hell!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnDe.Where is the Toma? Have you seen it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuBaEx^.The Toma Leolo is inside of there… I’ve been trying to get to it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnDe.Why do you care about it? How would you use it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx^.Thanks to you and Henry, my Guild is all but dead…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx^.That creepy statue can make me a new army… A better army.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.You’re insane! We’re going to destroy it!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.Is it locked? Why can’t you get it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.Where are the other demons? What is this place?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx^.It’s a temple… The little ones use it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnOp.This is crazy. Let’s get that Toma and get out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnDe^.What makes you think you can reach it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Duncan… You’re crazy. Lilith is not going to let you use the Toma to make an army.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlDe^.On the contrary, that’s exactly the plan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnEx.Enough chitchat. Keep an eye on Duncan… I’ll pick the lock.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx^.I’m not going anywhere… Be my guest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFrEx.I told you it would be no big deal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.So, now what? Are you going to sell it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElBaOp.I have no idea. But this place is a treasure trove.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnDe.We’re already in Hell… If I kill him, where will he go?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnEx.Unless you know how to open that gate, leave me alone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.You and I can be kings, 1Hero… And Lilith will be our queen.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp.The longer this takes, the riskier it gets.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "You can now find this character profile in your album.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoEx.Now let’s get the hell out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaDe.How do we know the Toma is actually inside that box?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrFlDe.I have an idea of how we can figure it out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx^.Why don’t you look inside and see, Johnson?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx^.I know it’s the Toma. You have no choice but to trust me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx.Enough arguing. If it’s not the Toma, we’re screwed anyway. We can’t stay here forever.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnEx.Shut up. You’re lucky we didn't kill you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlAnEx^.Mother… Daemalius will reveal his true form… He won’t be easy to trap.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlBaDe.We need help. He’s going to leave Erica’s body… He’ll be stronger without it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.My body? I’m not in my body now?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlBaEx.You’re a soul, young lady. You need an Earthly body to leave Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlBaEx.He must be trapped. He is otherwise immortal in this realm.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.How can we do anything against a demon in his own home?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlBaEx.As long as the doors to this temple remain shut, no demon can enter or leave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlBaDe^.Safer here than anywhere else in this place.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlAnEx^.Of course. He will gain more power without the human dragging him down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaEx.I will bring Erica to her body. 1Hero, you focus on distracting that demon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlAnEx.Father… Go with Erica’s soul… Find the body and destroy the Toma.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlMaOp^.What!? We will do no such thing!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlAnEx.Daemalius wants it! And when he gets it, he will not hesitate to turn Earth into a realm of zombies.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.Just kill him! Why are we stalling?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnAg^.We need that rock! What about my army?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlAnEx.Bless the statue with holy water while in the hands of the witch… Erica.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlAnEx.It will shatter into six pieces and will no longer take the souls of humans.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlMaOp^.What about the plan? I didn’t bring you to Earth for nothing!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlAnOp.Watch it! The plan is going forward… without the Toma.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlAnOp.Trust me. I’ve been here since the beginning of time. I know what’s being sacrificed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I’ll use the other one on the Toma once we find Erica.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFrEx^.I’m going too. I want to fight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaEx.Diana… Stay with Duncan. I will go.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlMaOp.Shit… I can’t go out there without you, Lilith.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlAnEx^.Stay here. I will meet him in my own body.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LlMaAg.We’re coming out, Daemalius… And we’re bringing the Toma with us.");
